quran[63]{c,v,t}:
  76,19,Ndipo adzazunguliridwa ndi ana owatumikira a misinkhu yofanana. Ndipo ngati iwe utawaona ukhoza kuganiza kuti ndi ndolo zomwazikamwazika
  76,20,"Ndipo pamene iwe uona kumeneko, udzaona madalitso ndi ufumu waukulu"
  76,21,Iwo adzavala nsalu zokongola za silika zooneka ngati msipu zopetedwa ndi golide. Iwo adzavala zibangiri za siliva ndipo Ambuye wawo adzawapatsa chakumwa chabwino
  76,22,Ndithudi iyi ndi mphotho yanu ndipo kupirira kwanu kwalandiridwa
  76,23,"Ndithudi ndife amene tavumbulutsa kwa iwe pang’ono pang’ono, Buku lolemekezeka la Korani"
  76,24,Motero pirira ndipo tsatira malamulo a Ambuye wako ndipo usamvere zonena za munthu wochimwa kapena wosakhulupirira amene ali pakati pawo
  76,25,Ndipo uzilemekeza dzina la Ambuye wako m’mawa ndi madzulo
  76,26,"Ndi m’gawo lina la usiku, uzimupembedza Iye ndipo uzimulemekeza Iye usiku wonse"
  76,27,"Ndithudi! Awa amakonda kwambiri moyo wa msanga msanga wa masiku ano, ndipo amaiwala tsiku limenelidzakhalalovuta"
  76,28,"Ndifeamenetidawalengandipo tinaika mphamvu m’ziwalo zawo. Koma ngati Ife titafuna, tikhoza kulenga anthu ena kuti alowe m’malo mwawo"
  76,29,"Ndithudi! Ili ndi chenjezo motero aliyense amene afuna, mulekeni kuti atsatire njira yoyenera yopita kwa Ambuye wake"
  76,30,Koma inu simudzatha kutero pokhapokha ndi chifuniro cha Mulungu. Ndithudi Mulungu ndiye Mwini kudziwa ndi Mwini nzeru
  76,31,"Iye adzaonetsa chisomo chake kwa aliyense amene Iye wamufuna. Koma anthu ochimwa, Iye wawakonzera iwo chilango chowawa"
  77,1,Pali mphepo imene imatsatana pafupipafupi
  77,2,Pali mphepo ya mkuntho
  77,3,Pali mphepo imene imamwaza mitambo ndi mvula
  77,4,Pali mavesi amene amasiyanitsa chabwino
  77,5,Pali angelo amene amabweretsa chivumbulutso kwa Atumwi
  77,6,Kuthetsa kukangana kapena kuwachenjeza
  77,7,Ndithudi zonse zimene mwalonjezedwa zidzachitika
  77,8,Pamene nyenyezi zidetsedwa
  77,9,Ndi pamene thambo la kumwamba ling’ambika pakati
  77,10,Ndi pamene mapiri aphwanyika kukhala fumbi
  77,11,Ndi pamene Atumwi onse asonkhanitsidwa kukhala pamalo amodzi
  77,12,Kodi ndi tsiku liti limene izi zidzachitike
  77,13,Lidzakhala tsiku la chiweruzo
  77,14,Kodi ndi chiyani chidzakudziwitse zatsiku la chiweruzo
  77,15,Tsoka pa tsiku limeneli kwa anthu osakhulupirira
  77,16,Kodi Ife sitinaononge anthu a makedzana
  77,17,Kotero tidzaipanga mibadwo yotsatira kuti ione zomwezo
  77,18,Mmenemu ndi mmene timakhaulitsira anthu ochita zoipa
  77,19,Tsoka pa tsikuli kwa anthu osakhulupirira
  77,20,Kodi sitidakulengeni inu kuchokera ku madzi onyozeka
  77,21,Amene tidasunga pamalo okhazikika
  77,22,Mpaka nthawi yake itakwana
  77,23,Motero Ife tinayesa ndipo Ife wodziwa kuyesa
  77,24,Tsoka pa tsikuli kwa anthu osakhulupirira
  77,25,Kodi Ife sitinapange nthaka ngati malo okumaniranamo
  77,26,Amoyo ndi akufa
  77,27,"Ndipo tidalenga Al Mursalat\t635 mapiri atali pa dziko ndi kukupatsani madzi okoma kuti muzimwa"
  77,28,Tsoka pa tsikuli kwa anthu osakhulupirira
  77,29,"(Zidzanenedwa kuti): “Pitani ku chilango chimene munkati sichidzabwera!”"
  77,30,"Pitani inu mu chithunzi, mu magulu atatu"
  77,31,Opanda mthunzi kapena pokhala pokutetezani ku malawi a moto
  77,32,Ndithudi! Umatulutsa malawi ake akulu akulu ngati nyumba zachifumu
  77,33,Ndipo ooneka ngati ngamira ya chikasu
  77,34,Tsoka pa tsiku limeneli kwa anthu osakhulupirira
  77,35,Patsiku limeneli iwo sadzatha kulankhula
  77,36,Ndipo sadzaloledwa kuti apereke chidandaulo
  77,37,Tsoka pa tsiku limeneli kwa anthu osakhulupirira
  77,38,Limeneli ndilo tsiku la chiweruzo. Ife takusonkhanitsani nonse pamodzi ndi anthu a makedzana
  77,39,"Tsopano ngati inu muli ndi chiwembu, chitani chiwembu chanu kwa Ine"
  77,40,Tsoka pa tsiku limeneli kwa anthu osakhulupirira
  77,41,Ndithudi anthu angwiro adzakhala mu mthunzi wozizira ndi pa akasupe
  77,42,Ndi zipatso zimene afuna kukhosi kwawo
  77,43,Idyani ndipo imwani mosangalala chifukwa cha zimene mudachita
  77,44,"Ndithudi, mmenemo ndi mmene timalipirira anthu angwiro"
  77,45,Tsoka pa tsikuli kwa anthu osakhulupirira
  77,46,Idyani ndipo musangalale kwa kanthawi kochepa. Ndithudi inu ndinu oipa kwambiri
  77,47,Tsoka pa tsikuli kwa anthu osakhulupirira
  77,48,"Ndipo zikanenedwa kwa iwo kuti: “Weramani.” Iwo amakana kutero"
  77,49,Tsoka pa tsikuli kwa anthu osakhulupirira
  77,50,Kodi ndi Uthenga uti woposa uwu umene adzaukhulupirire